# Email        : rick.romig@gmail.com | rick.romig@mymetronet.net
# Created      : 09 Jan 2022
# Updated      : 09 Feb 2026
# Comments     : Use install-batcat if distro version has same base version number as latest GitHub release.
#              : Mint 22 installs version 0.24.0 with the Ubuntu version appended.
#              : Debian 13 installs version 0.25.0 with the Debian version appended.
#              : LMDE 7 (stable) installs version 0.22.1-4.
# TODO (Rick)  :
# License      : GNU General Public License, version 2.0
# License URL  : https://github.com/RickRomig/scripts/blob/main/LICENSE
